          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The secondary beam 17F was produced by the",
                "2H(16O,17F)n reaction. After the reaction, the",
                "secondary beam 17F was separated, purified, and",
                "transported by RIBLL to the secondary target chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A self-supported 208Pb target (2.0 mg/cm2 thick)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two plastic scintillators (C9H10) with a",
                "thickness of 10.16 um were installed in the beam line",
                "to give the time of flight (TOF) information.",
                "Behind the 208Pb target along the beam line a plastic",
                "scintillator with an active area of 40 X 40 mm2 and",
                "a thickness of 5 mm was installed to monitor the beam",
                "intensity. Its signals were read out by the",
                "multi-pixel photo counter (MPPC)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PPAC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two parallel plate avalanche counters (PPAC)",
                "were installed at 984 mm and 290 mm in front of the",
                "208Pb target, respectively."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH",
                "SISD",
                "SI",
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " There are ten detector units",
                "around the 208Pb target, each unit contains one grid",
                "ionization chamber (IC), one double-sided silicon",
                "strip detector (DSSD), and two-quadrant silicon",
                "detectors (QSD). By using this design, heavy ions can",
                "be discriminated easily by the IC-DSSD combined",
                "telescopes, and light particles can be distinguished",
                "by the following two QSDs."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The TOF method was used to identify the beam",
                "particles."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Depending on two projected energy spectra, the",
                "conditions of selecting the scattered 17F can be",
                "determined."
              ]
            }
          ],
